page.title: 18A schoolday in Edenthorpe.
page.content: {7.45am} As they say,"the early morning bird gets the worm first" but that's not me! Anyway, I go and get a wash, brush my teeth and get dressed. Then I go downstairs and have an argument with my mum because I won't have any breakfast. {8.30am} Set off to school and get there about twenty to nine. When it is time we go in for registration. Then on a Thursday we have single Games, followed by single Geography, and after break we have French.{Then dinner.} {1.20pm} Back for registration, then double maths, afternoon break, followed by Design. We go home at {4.00pm.} {6.30pm} Get ready for the disco. {10.00pm}Set off home. Then go to bed.
